These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, electrician
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, scooter
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the software-developer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing       | puzzles |
| Job         | electrician | software-developer  |
| Sport       | snowboarding    | sailing    |
| Transport   | scooter       | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, fisherman
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, family
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, climbing
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the teacher is on the far left##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | fanta |
| Job           | teacher | fisherman      |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | musical      |
| Sport         | volleyball | climbing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate
There 2 different types of food: tomato, orange
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, house
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, motorbike
1. the fan of house is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking cola is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | cola | hot-chocolate  |
| Food          | tomato    | orange   |
| Music-Genre   | house  | punk   |
| Transport     | motorbike     | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
