There 2 different types of food: banana, blueberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, entrepreneur
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, folk
1. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
2. the manager is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
