1. the japanese is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
3. the japanese is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | garlic | pear |
| Music-Genre   | house     | disco      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | japanese    |
| Pet           | hamster    | ferret    |

